## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **evolocumab + alirocumab 2015** = first PCSK9 mAb. LDL-C 추가 60% ↓ (statin + ezetimibe 위에). FOURIER 2017 + ODYSSEY OUTCOMES 2018 CV outcome positive. quantum-VQE 의 PCSK9 + LDLR PPI interface 가 직접 fit.
2. **inclisiran Leqvio 2021** = first PCSK9 siRNA — twice-yearly subQ (compliance paradigm shift). GalNAc-conjugated. quantum-VQE 의 RNA-oligonucleotide design + cross-iag platform.
3. **bempedoic acid Nexletol 2020** = first ATP-citrate lyase inhibitor. statin-intolerant alternative + CLEAR Outcomes 2023 CV positive. quantum-VQE 의 ATP-citrate lyase pocket leverage.
4. **evinacumab Evkeeza 2021** = first ANGPTL3 mAb. HoFH 적응증. ANGPTL3 LoF homozygote = healthy → genetic validation 강력. quantum-VQE 의 ANGPTL3-LPL/EL interface fit.
5. **olezarsen Tryngolza 2024** = first FDA APOC3 ASO. FCS (familial chylomicronemia syndrome) 적응증. volanesorsen 2019 EU 후 FDA 첫 진입. apoC-III ↓ → LPL activation. quantum-VQE 의 ASO design + apoC-III mRNA target.
6. **obicetrapib (research, NewAmsterdam) 2024** = first CETP HDL paradigm 부활. torcetrapib 2006 + dalcetrapib 2012 + evacetrapib 2017 + anacetrapib 2017 모두 실패 후. PRESERVE 2024 + BROADWAY 2024. quantum-VQE 의 CETP pocket ranking 가 기존 4 실패 history 와 새 obicetrapib 비교 학습.
7. **arc-1 (olpasiran Arrowhead/Amgen) + lepodisiran (Lilly) + pelacarsen (Ionis/Novartis) 2024** = Lp(a) target 3 platform Phase 3 동시. Lp(a) HORIZON 2025 readout 기다림. lipoprotein(a) 가 genetic CV risk factor + 기존 약리 없음 → first-in-class 경쟁.
8. **statin 7-class 1987-2009** = simvastatin + atorvastatin + rosuvastatin + lovastatin + pravastatin + pitavastatin + fluvastatin. mega-blockbuster era + LDL-C target 70 + 55 mg/dL paradigm (ESC 2019 + ACC/AHA 2018).
9. **ezetimibe 2002 + IMPROVE-IT 2014** = NPC1L1 cholesterol absorption + statin 위 추가 LDL-C 24% ↓. 첫 non-statin LDL-C 외 임상 outcome benefit. quantum-VQE 의 NPC1L1 pocket fit.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, lipidology 임상 의미 한정. obicetrapib + Lp(a) 3 platform readout 2025 = paradigm shift 잠재.

